Achievements.Name: The n00b Run
Achievements.Description: Complete the tutorial mission of the Lyrius campaign.

Achievements.Name: Smash 'n Grab
Achievements.Description: Destroy all red crates in a mission. Cannot be completed in tutorial mission.

Achievements.Name: Commanding The Bridge
Achievements.Description: Dock the GCV Starguard with Arkangel station.

Achievements.Name: Getting Things Done
Achievements.Description: Complete the first 8 missions of the Lyrius Campaign.

Achievements.Name: Vets And Victory
Achievements.Description: Complete all Lyrius campaign missions on Normal.

Achievements.Name: Heroes End
Achievements.Description: Complete all Lyrius campaign missions on Hard.

Achievements.Name: Certified
Achievements.Description: Purchase your first CTC.

Achievements.Name: Jack of All Trades
Achievements.Description: Unlock all CTCs on a single character.

Achievements.Name: Ready For Anything
Achievements.Description: Unlock all weapons, CTCs and items on a single character.

Achievements.Name: Flawless Execution
Achievements.Description: Complete a mission without taking damage.

Achievements.Name: Close Quarters Mayhem
Achievements.Description: Eliminate 20 Insurgents using melee combat.

Achievements.Name: Sniper Elite
Achievements.Description: Eliminate 100 Insurgents with sniper head shots.

Achievements.Name: Aerial Warfare
Achievements.Description: Use 10 airstrikes.

Achievements.Name: The Life Saver
Achievements.Description: Perform 25 uses of the Medical Kit.

Achievements.Name: Human Clone
Achievements.Description: Perform 25 BIO-HUMAN revives.

Achievements.Name: Asteroids
Achievements.Description: Destroy 20 asteroids.

Achievements.Name: Behind Enemy Lines
Achievements.Description: Kill 40 or more enemies in a single skirmish.

Achievements.Name: Duty and Honor
Achievements.Description: Complete all secondary and optional objectives in the campaign.

Achievements.Name: Ground Warfare
Achievements.Description: Eliminate 10 Insurgent vehicles during campaign missions.

Achievements.Name: Engineering Corps
Achievements.Description: Perform 10 uses of the Repair Kit.
